{"tid":1447014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔係唔勇武，但係要用腦］［忠言逆耳］影響香港經濟可能比起打狗更有用！為咗道氣去日日圍狗局真係有好大作用？","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:30.000Z","uid":137493,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0096f7848a16026bdb758ec0f156bfe476b8bc","tid":1447014,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"死守之後被狗捉，第二日香港一樣係咁，要影響經濟，中共/港府先會驚，畀你上次認到係假示威者又可以點，唔通次次都認到/捉到？<br />\n<br />\n機場係香港經濟命脈最緊要既一環，只要空管一罷工，當日取消最少3分2飛機，好多貨去唔到香港，即係轉運唔到，啲公司一定會賠錢。最少人手有最大效果，何樂而不為？"},{"pid":"6a470a21a93797ec230d30b7bb78dcee8681317a","tid":1447014,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d542c0d3f8615382ffae8cea23163620bc36f06f","tid":1447014,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"469f9b9c95fccc12f0da2faf1f51552bef991893","tid":1447014,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0bfa4a8891436bb6e7d912c2df23cbd58a0734d0","tid":1447014,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<